```rust
#[utoipa::path(/* ... */)]
pub async fn handler(
    State(state): State<Arc<AuthState>>,
    auth: AuthContext,
) -> Result<Json<ResponseDto>, ApiError> {
    auth.require_permission(&Permission::X)?;
    // Implementation
    Ok(Json(response))
}
```

**Graceful Shutdown:**

```rust
tokio::select! {
    _ = shutdown_rx.recv() => {
